			That's it! Check out my snippets, or contribute your own. If you'd like to check out the work I have, you can view my <a href="https://github.com/dylanthelion">github profile</a>. If you're viewing this within a few weeks of my initial hosting, there may not be much to see on this site, but there will be more to come. 
		</p>
